stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending : checkout created
    Pending --> AwaitingPayment : booking saved
    AwaitingPayment --> ProofSubmitted : customer uploads proof
    ProofSubmitted --> Pending : admin rejects proof
    ProofSubmitted --> Confirmed : admin approves (partial pay)
    ProofSubmitted --> Completed : admin approves (fully paid)
    Confirmed --> ProofSubmitted : customer submits another proof
    Confirmed --> Completed : remaining balance approved
    Pending --> Cancelled : customer/admin cancels
    AwaitingPayment --> Cancelled : timeout / cancel
    Completed --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
